{"tid":643002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]巴士上見到張紙 有冇人睇得明佢寫乜?_?","createTime":"2018-04-26T07:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T11:25:27.000Z","uid":108674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d66a37d4af159a993ce1de48e76ae7cf302883","tid":643002,"uid":108674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"巴士上本身諗住訓 但係見到張咁嘅嘢貼咗喺櫈下面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/153506_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F153506_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a46e415b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗貼到咁肯定係啲on9中二病小學雞玩埋啲咩密碼尋寶之類嗰啲啦......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是我就憑著密碼裡的提示踏上偉大航路展開我嘅旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之張紙寫咗啲咁嘅嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/153518_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F153518_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=35cd30bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老味完全睇唔明寫乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打知道佢寫咩 我可以分10%寶藏俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3f1bb0cb08e2c7fca3be756def048466fcda04","tid":643002,"uid":96877,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"你講野好撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"6b53c5d13212e0b45302bfe3997b405f0858164c","tid":643002,"uid":10671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-